parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Thank you for helping. I hope whatever you’ve found isn’t harmful to your health.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuHaOp.Isn’t it lovely? So much nicer than my previous church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuBaEx.It was a part of Saint Dame University.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.I’ve known Chloe for a long time…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.You know her from college, don’t you?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.I was a counselor at the school.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.That was a hell of a mystery, I heard.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I mean… What happened at Saint Dame University… It must have been hard for you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaOp.What happened in the past can not be changed... ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx.But perhaps a new future can be made here in North Santiva.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.If you don’t mind, I’d love to check out the storage area.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.Are you sure you saw her come into the chapel?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoOp.It sounded like it came from the attic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.Is that chandelier supposed to be swinging?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl>.I’m sorry I left you, 1Hero… I was frightened.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I think I found the cause of your noises...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoOp.1Hero. I still feel our safety is in jeopardy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I think you’re feeling lonely here… all by yourself.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoOp.Perhaps you’re right. But something has happened recently…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.I can’t put my finger on it…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.But darkness has fallen over this city. I can feel it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.If anything comes up, give us a call and we’ll be here to help you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.If you don’t mind, I should probably get going.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Oh, I’m sure you have a busy schedule.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlEx.Such is the life of an investigator.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Good luck with the church, Father Solomon.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Maybe you’ll join us for evening Mass?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I don’t know. I’ll probably be working.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.It looks like it could fall at any moment.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.It’s just a matter of time. And if someone is under it when it falls, that’s a hell of a way to go.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I came by to say hi to Chloe.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx>.Uh, yes. We heard it from the chapel.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.Do you know how to fix rigging cable, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I’ve done things like it in the past.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.There may be maintenance manuals somewhere in the church, but I don’t know where.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl>.Can we fix it without the proper instructions?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Leave it to me. I know what to do.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaEx.I’d hate to take your time on the weekend.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx.It’s not a problem for 1Hero. He loves working weekends.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Once you get the proper equipment, come see me. I’ll help you install it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Do you want to study with us?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I just thought I’d join you two.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx.Judy was just about to tell me a story.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.It’s okay, Sister Judy. I can leave.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFlEx.Come on. Tell me all the juicy details.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp.Thank you for helping us fix the broken rigging cable.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Come back when you have a restored rigging cable and I’ll help you set it up.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.We should be able to use this rigging cable to fix the swinging chandelier.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Thanks for helping us fix the church. Now if only you can fix our attendance problems.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlOp.I’m not sure I can help you with that one.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.Why would Judy leave her clothes on the floor like this?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeBaDe.Let’s hope not all of Zephaniah’s belongings ended up in the garbage.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl^.Oh no! What if she tells Father?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I don’t think that’s going to happen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChSaDe.I know… But we can’t take it back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx^.That woman thinks we were having sex. She doesn’t know it was not inside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx^.Should I tell her that we didn’t have real sex. She must know it’s not real sex.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoEx.Don’t worry about it. She’s not the type to tattle.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.It’s my fault. Let’s just leave it at that… You did nothing wrong Sister Judy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoCl.So… You watched the door the whole time?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I should get going and leave you two alone.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp^.Is your mind freed from the dirty thoughts, Chloe?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrCl.Oh, yeah… My mind is clear. I’m ready to study with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx^.Mass will be here tomorrow morning. Let’s not think too much about this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrEx^.And 1Hero. If you could please let Nellie know that we were not having real sex, that would be much appreciated.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoClNo1^.Ah! Yes! Don’t tell him… He wouldn’t understand… He’s not a woman.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnCl^.Dammit… Judy pressed so damn hard on my cock.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaDe^.It’s not her fault. She didn’t know…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I suggest not wandering too far behind the church.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.I thought we were too far north for those.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeHaOp.Judy here has shown me so much. I had no idea the church was so big.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx^.Yes. It’s very dark. We only discovered it last week.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This area seems to hold a lot of secrets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.Did you find something else on your hike?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx^.God saw all that he had made, and it was very good. And there was evening, and there was morning…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx@^.Then the Lord God made a woman from the rib he had taken from Adam, and he brought her to him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrOp^.This is now bone of my bones and flesh of my flesh.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaEx^.The man called his wife's name Eve, because she was the mother of all living.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx^.In conclusion, we are all the children of Eve. The chosen mother of humanity.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrHaEx^.Next week, I’ll tell you all about how she got hoodwinked by a talking snake.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.If you find something, bring it to me. I can determine if it’s a genuine holy relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I found something that might be a relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I found something that might be a relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I found something that might be a relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.I must… get close to the darkness.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.I must not sin… But I must get close… If the relic is genuine, I will feel pain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl.That may just make it more dangerous.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoCl.1Hero! That will turn me into a demon!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArWoEx.Watch the doors. Make sure no one comes inside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.You know what you need to do, Arianna.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaDe.I… I know. I risk much doing this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaDe.Erica should be in the Empyrean… We should not send her to Hell.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.She was never meant to look at the Toma. Bring her back to Earth.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Let’s bring her to a safer place.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArSaOp.I feel no pain… I’m afraid this relic is not genuine.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ArFrEx.If you find something, bring it to me. I can determine if it’s a genuine holy relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I found something that might be a relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I found something that might be a relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.I found something that might be a relic.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrMaAg.I command you, unclean spirit, leave this holy place!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DjMaCl>.Looks like my time here is done.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFlOp.Hot damn, I must have missed one hell of a show.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Father! I found a piece of the Toma Leolo!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl^.That monster… It made me say things I shouldn’t have said.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrAnDe.What is this Toma Leolo? Are you collecting cursed artifacts and bringing them to the church, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I didn’t know it was cursed… I’m sorry.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.So it’s true… There are magical artifacts in North Santiva!");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It’s… Lillian claims to be trying to save another world from chaos…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoOp.I know it sounds crazy… But she says she needs the Toma Leolo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.You’re being deceived. I can sense it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.No… I’ve seen it. There is another world outside of ours.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoCl.Oh, my God. Is this all part of the thief case you’re working on?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I don’t know how it all connects. But I know I can figure it out. You have to trust me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.The Lord has brought me to North Santiva for a reason…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe.The Guild and now the demonic world are colliding here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.I don’t know what to do. But Lillian is planning something. She’s even going to have Kimberly Foxx report on it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrShOp.She wants a reporter to tell the city about another realm of existence?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.It sounds crazy. But she wants to complete the Toma and show the world a rift to another plane of existence.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoDe.The news lady committed to doing something that crazy?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.There must be a rational explanation for this.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx^.I know of nothing but demonic powers that could have produced what we just experienced.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrSaEx.You’re in over your head, 1Hero. You need my help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.I’m going to find out what this Toma Leolo is all about.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.It’s of Casula origin. You should talk to Erica.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.Bring her here. We need to get to the bottom of this before you help Lillian. I don’t trust her, and you shouldn’t either.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I know… I know… It’s hard to know what to do… It’s like my mind is being pulled in different directions.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.You need to follow your heart, 1Hero. You’ve always been good at this kind of thing.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.I will keep you safe, and you can help me study. ");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp.How many of those artifacts do you need to find, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.I have four of them now, with one left in the mansion…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.There’s only one piece left to find.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx.If you find it, keep it secret.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.This is crazy, 1Hero. It doesn't seem real.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I know the thought. It was hard for me to believe, too.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Chloe already knows about the Toma Leolo.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaOp.I meant about what we just did…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Oh, right. I don’t know… Maybe we should keep it a secret.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaEx.That was the last time, Heather… There’s nothing left to say.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeSaDe.Isn’t there? The monster knew our innermost secrets.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaEx.I should go find the girls. I want to keep an eye on them.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Don’t worry. Everything's going to be okay.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.Could Father have put it in a storage box? Maybe it’s hidden.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaShOp.Wow! I bet it costs a fortune to heat this place in the winter.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaAnEx.Chloe is showing us the cathedral. Show some manners.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoCl^.You don’t want to mess with an alligator.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx^.Come on, Hannah. I’ll go into the woods with you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Be careful – there really is an alligator back there.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.Yeah. I guess we’ve had warmer weather this year.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CaBaEx.And a hell of a lot of storms.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChFrEx^.Come on, Carol. I’ll show you the view.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HnHaEx.Come with us, 1Hero! You can help us wrangle the gator.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Don’t joke about that, Hannah. That thing will eat you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx^.Come on, Hannah. I want to see this alligator.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrEx.Don’t worry about it. Just detective work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.I can see a torn page up there. I wonder if I could throw something at it and knock it down.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.It’s a torn page… But without the other pieces, I can't read what it says.");
